# Trivy CVE exceptions for orkyo-community
# Format: CVE-YYYY-NNNNN  # Impact | Reason | Added: YYYY-MM-DD | Review: YYYY-MM-DD
# (no exceptions at initial setup)

# ── Keycloak base image (quay.io/keycloak/keycloak:26.6.1 / ubi9) ────────────
# The Keycloak image ships without a package manager; OS packages cannot be
# upgraded from within the Dockerfile. These CVEs are in the upstream ubi9 base
# and require Keycloak to publish a new image with an updated base.
# Review when keycloak > 26.6.1 is available.

# java-21-openjdk-headless — Oracle CPU 2025-07 / 2026-01 / 2026-04 patches
